channel.title: DefianceX Looking For: Web Designer!
channel.description:
[center]DefianceX Looking For:
[s]Host[/s] [s]Staff[/s] [s]Coder[/s] Web Designer
DefianceX brings about a new era within the RSPS regime. We're a multi-lingual, multi-platform RSPS. Perfection would be an understatement. We offer 25 unique skills tailored to our players pleasing. Not to mention countless hours spent programming nearly flawless skills, including Dungeoneering, our developers at DefianceX have also taken the time to create custom items to further engage our players! Our staff positions are not sold, we would much rather promote the honest and dedicated players of DefianceX. [/center]
HOSTER: [s]We are looking for a host to keep the server up 24/7 for the time being. We will be buying our own VPS with the donations that come to the server. Host will be Owner of the server.[/s]
STAFF: [s]We need mature and loyal staff that will help people when ever on. You must be mature and know your way around a RSPS. We are looking for 1 Head Admin and 1 Mod [/s]
CODER: [s]We are looking for a mature coder. Coder must have had past experience with RSPS 317. Will receive Co-Owner ***MUST HAVE TEAMVIEWER!*** (We had a coder but he quit on us out of the blue. We have a source with a custom home. Looking for a coder that can just finish the job.)[/s]
WEB DESIGNER: We will be starting off with a free website platform. In the process of us growing, we will be buying a website domain. Rank will be decided
Application:
[Code] WebDesigner- Name: Age: Skype: How Active Are You on the computer: How Long Have You Been Playing Rsps?: Past Experience: [/Code]
[center][shadow=red,left]Owner: Jason
Staff- Admin: Matt
CODER: Shame
Web Designer: ???[/shadow][/center]
[CENTER]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2TIDZ0-93J0[/CENTER]
[left] Features: Summoning, Dungeoneering, and all other skills working! Summoning familiars, pets Charms from monsters, and Summoning shop 3 fully completeable quests 27 fully completeable achievements Construction skill, building stuff Full GWD with Nex! Custom mini-games Dupe fixes Overloads New gameframe etc. Changed a lot interfaces to better ones Dungeoneering with NPCs, killcount, rewards shop! GWD and Dungeoneering NPCs Dungeoneering and new GWD items Pest Control with rewards shop Hunter with implings and looting Mage Bank with rewards shop JAD (Fire cape) Corporeal Beast Evil Spirit (Wildy boss) King Black Dragon Barrelchest guardian Gnome and Wildy agility course All RC altars All skillcape emotes working (Dung too!) Better bank, shop, trade etc. interfaces Working GS, SS, PvP, SoL and other weapon specs Pk, Mage Bank, Multi PvP, Fun PK Sprit Shields with effects! DFS special Full PvP, Primal, Promethium, Zephyrium, Torva, Virtus, Pernix, Dragon (g), Soulbell and more armors with correct stats Some great and awesome shops! Custom Donator zone with shops, skilling and monsters And even more that I can't remember[/left]
[center] PICTURES:
